songs.title: Ready To Go
songs.album: A Collection of Rare and Unreleased Recordings
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
All these thoughts of you and me are driving me crazy
When I see you all I need just a kiss then you're chasing me
I know you got your girl but I think shes diggin me
So if you're not so scared to share your toys play with me
I'm not the type to leave you dancing alone
I like her style she more then welcome to come
I know you will so don't act like you want
I see it in your eyes and she's already gone

[Chorus]
Oh (ready to go)
Oh (ready to go)
Oh (ready to go)
Oh (ready to go)

[Verse 2]
Don't you turn me off cause kiss and talents for rookies
If you want me now behind me because ill fulfill your needs
I'm bringing out the best parts of everybody
The nights stick together like we do in our dreams
I'm not the type to make a scene so I won't
But you keep looking at me turning me on
I don't mind she and come if she can roll
Let's ditch this place I'm ready to go

[Chorus]
Oh (ready to go)
Oh (ready to go)
Oh (ready to go)
Oh (ready to go)

[Verse 2]
No need to rush it baby we got all night
If you're uncomfortable just saying the word ill make it right
The only rule is to do whatever you like
But tell me are you ready for me tonight
Oh oh oh

[Chorus]
Oh (ready to go)
Oh (ready to go)
Oh (ready to go)
Oh (ready to go)

[Outro]
Ready to go
I see it in your eyes and she's all ready to go
Ready to go
I see it in your eyes and she's all ready to go
